European Stocks Decline; Stoxx 600 Index Falls for First Time in Four Days

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-03-22T15:00:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-22/european-stocks-decline-stoxx-600-index-falls-for-first-time-in-four-days.html
European stocks fell, erasing
earlier gains, as oil surged in  New York  and Greek and Irish
bonds retreated.  The Stoxx Europe 600 Index dropped 0.4 percent to 271.19 at
2:59 p.m. in  London , the first decline in four days.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at 
 arummer@bloomberg.net  